/* PreviewKit — English (en) localization.

   Keys are organized by namespace. Renderers read via
   `PKL10n.<Namespace>.<key>` (typed wrapper) which falls through to
   `String(localized: ..., bundle: .module)`. The host application's
   preferred locale picks the matching .lproj at runtime — no host
   configuration required.

   When adding a new key:
   1. Add it here.
   2. Add the matching translation in every other lproj/.strings.
   3. Surface it through the typed `PKL10n` enum so renderers don't
      stringly-type the key path.
*/

